                <p>Luck.</p>
            </div>
        </TabPage>
        <TabPage TabLabel="Match Procedure">
            <ul>
                <li>Join the match lobby.</li>
                <li class="nested-list">
                    <ul>
                        <li>The password will be provided via stream chat and discord.</li>
                        <li><b>Do Not</b> join the last team on the list unless you are playing the role of the landshark. It would defeat the purpose of the game.</li>
                    </ul>
                </li>                
            </ul>

            <div class="winCondition">

                <p><b>Win Conditions</b></p>
                <p>The winner is the one to land the punch that 'knocks' the shark. (Try not killing them)</p>
                <p><b>OR</b></p>
                <p>The shark wins if they survive the entire match time.</p>

            </div>
        </TabPage>

        <TabPage TabLabel="Rules of Engagement">
            <ul>
                <li>As the landshark, <b>Do Not</b> purposefully leave the hunting ground limits.</li>
                <li>As the landshark, <b>Do Not</b> use the ascenders as hiding spots.</li>
            </ul>
